{"tid":468165,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有村架純冧莊　孖二宮和也做《紅白》司儀","createTime":"2017-11-14T06:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T14:45:08.000Z","uid":76329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9c450dfa1e901e2fc8745b3b6b63316b82fb1f33","tid":468165,"uid":76329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"日本NHK電視台年度音樂大騷《第68回紅白歌唱大賽》，將於今年大除夕舉行。NHK今日公布紅白兩組司儀名單，今年主演晨早劇《雛鳥》收視有功的24歲當紮女星有村架純，冧莊再任紅組司儀。而尊尼組合嵐成員二宮和也接隊友相葉雅紀棒，首次擔任白組司儀。<br />\n<br />\n有村對於再做《紅白》司儀感到驚訝，她表示雖然有不足之處，但為了不失禮所有表演者及工作人員，自己亦會努力以赴。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171113/photo/bkn-20171113161955998-1113_00862_001_01b.jpg?20171113164542\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171113161955998-1113_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20171113164542&h=82dfa71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171113/photo/bkn-20171113161955998-1113_00862_001_02p.jpg?20171113164542\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171113161955998-1113_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20171113164542&h=36255b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有村架純去年拍住相葉雅紀做主持，今年再擔任司儀一職。"},{"pid":"9b08083e37fb5d012b27f966b09b04eba40ec2b7","tid":468165,"uid":48577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:47:21.000Z","msg":"變左正能量方塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751f16173d31609b3ce97ea18da840a759d2a48f","tid":468165,"uid":76329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>變左正能量方塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfac04428f3da35821c6ca874b5ed8ec18f4ca92","tid":468165,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":